project_descr: The project aims at contributing to improving the delivery of justice services through the establishment of a robust information system in the justice sector with full participation of CSO, professional associations and communities.

outputs.output_descr: The project aims at contributing to improving the delivery of justice services through the establishment of a robust information system in the justice sector that will enable an integrated  management of backlog cases throughout the justice chain.
